---
import { Sparkles } from "lucide-astro";
import { CTAActions } from "./CTAActions";
---

<section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden section-fade-top">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      {/* Efectos de fondo con el color PRIMARY de tu marca */}
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-purple-500/10 to-primary/10 rounded-3xl blur-3xl opacity-50"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"
        style="animation-delay: 1s;"
      >
      </div>

      {/* Tarjeta Principal */}
      <div
        class="relative bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-xl border border-primary/10 rounded-[2rem] p-10 md:p-16 text-center overflow-hidden shadow-2xl"
      >
        {/* Contenido */}
        <div class="relative z-10 mb-10">
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm font-medium mb-6 border border-primary/20"
          >
            <Sparkles class="w-4 h-4" />
            Da el siguiente paso
          </span>

          <h2
            class="font-orbitron text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-foreground mb-6 leading-tight"
          >
            ¿Tienes un proyecto en mente? <br />
            <span class="text-gradient-primary">Hagámoslo realidad.</span>
          </h2>

          <p
            class="font-inter text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
          >
            No te quedes con la duda. Agenda una sesión inicial gratuita y
            evaluemos juntos la viabilidad y el alcance de tu idea.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Botones Interactivos */}
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <CTAActions client:visible />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
